                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8545" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0910</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1690 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿色智造：赣州工业化绿色创新引领可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Green Smart Manufacturing: Ganzhou Industrialization&#39;s Green Innovation Leads Sustainable Development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">康丽群，孙伟，宋戈，曾思智，罗海平，麦群，朱春晖，刘宇辉</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南昌大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赣州建筑工业化有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿色创新；数字化能力；绿色动态能力；可持续发展；2024百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Green Innovation; Digital Capability; Green Dynamic Ability; Sustainable Development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿色创新是培育提升绿色生产力的新动能。赣州工业化在成立之初就确立了“绿色建筑智造商，装配产业领跑者”的经营理念以及“推进绿色创新，赋能可持续发展”的发展战略。在竞争压力上升、投资速度放缓、数字新基建兴起、利益相关者绿色期望强化情境下，赣州工业化通过坚持绿色创新战略，促使企业获取了规制合法性和战略合法性，实现了从新创企业到装配式绿色建筑示范引领企业的转变。赣州工业化绿色创新是在绿色动态能力驱动下，通过提升数字化能力，从而推动绿色管理创新、绿色工艺创新、绿色产品创新，进而实现财务绩效与环境绩效双赢的过程。通过对赣州工业化绿色创新的战略定力、具体举措、前因后果的剖析，期望为我国通过数字驱动的绿色创新改造提升传统工业企业以及提升传统产业合法性提供启示和借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Green innovation is the new driving force for cultivating and enhancing green productivity. From its inception, Ganzhou Industrialization has established the business philosophy of “green building smart manufacturer, assembly industry leader” and the development strategy of “promoting green innovation, empowering sustainable development.” In the context of increasing competitive pressure, slowing investment, the rise of digital new infrastructure, and strengthened green expectations from stakeholders, Ganzhou Industrialization has, by adhering to its green innovation strategy, enabled the company to gain regulatory legitimacy and strategic legitimacy, achieving the transformation from a newly established enterprise to a leading demonstration enterprise in prefabricated green buildings. The green innovation in Ganzhou Industrialization represents a strategic endeavor to attain a synergistic balance between financial and environmental performance, propelled by green dynamic capabilities and augmented through digital capabilities, thereby fostering innovations in green management, processes, and products. By analyzing the strategic determination, specific measures, causes, and consequences of Ganzhou Industrialization’s green innovation, it is hoped to provide insights and references for China’s transformation and enhancement of traditional industrial enterprises through digitally-driven green innovation, as well as for enhancing the legitimacy of traditional industries.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《技术创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织合法性理论；绿色创新的定义、维度与评价；绿色动态能力→数字化能力→绿色创新；绿色创新与企业可持续发展绩效的关系；战略学习→（工业互联网平台）数实融合→企业绿色创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
